description:
From the walls of Tehran to the podiums of Asia, Sarina Ghafari is rewriting the story of Iranian women in sport climbing.  
she’s already a multi-gold medalist in IFSC Youth Championships, dominating both Lead and Bouldering categories. Her explosive speed, precision, and fearless mindset have made her a global inspiration.  

Sarina isn’t just climbing walls—she’s breaking barriers. 🇮🇷💪  

 Follow her journey as she represents Iran on the international stage, proving that talent, discipline, and heart know no borders.  

📍Latest: IFSC Asian Cup Almaty 2025 – Speed Qualification  
🔥 Let’s celebrate the rise of a true champion.
